titles.title: A concurrent resolution correcting the enrollment of S.854, the Nevada-Florida Land Exchange Authorization Act of 1988.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.
Called up by House by Unanimous Consent.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 3/28/1988--Introduced. Makes corrections in the enrollment of S. 854 (Nevada-Florida Land Exchange Authorization Act of 1988).
